Global Permanent magnet powder Market Insights
Permanent magnet powder Market size was valued at USD 1.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Permanent Magnet Powder Market Overview
The global permanent magnet powder market was valued at approximately USD 2.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 4.3 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.2% during the forecast period. This market growth is primarily driven by the increasing demand for permanent magnets in automotive, electronics, and renewable energy sectors. The surge in electric vehicle production, the expansion of wind energy generation, and advancements in consumer electronics have collectively contributed to the heightened demand for high-performance permanent magnet powders. Key players in this market are focusing on expanding their product portfolios and regional footprints to capitalize on the rising demand.

